  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Missing Translations for Enrollment CTA Elements\n\nEnsure that the `ready_to_enroll` and `enroll_cta_description` text content within the `.cta-section` component is properly translated across all supported languages.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the `.cta-section` component in the codebase\n- Identify where `ready_to_enroll` and `enroll_cta_description` content is defined\n- Add these strings to the translation files for all supported locales\n- Update the component to use the translation system (e.g., i18n, translation keys)\n- Verify translations appear correctly for each language\n- Test that language switching updates these elements dynamically\n- Ensure fallback behavior if translation is missing",
